Sofare: aha ya sitere na Société de Fabrication de Rétrochargeurs maọbụ Company Manufacturing backhoe loaders bụ enyemaka nke ENMTP, nke nwere isi obodo edebanyere aha nke ijeri DZD 2 ọkachamara na-emepụta backhoe loadors, Compaction Equipment, Stationary Compressors ya na Concrete injection pump.
SOFARE mepụtara compactors nke ngwaahịa Ọgbọ Ọhụrụ site na enyemaka ya Europactor Algeria nke e kere dịka njikọ aka, na mmekorita ya na ụlọ ọrụ nke ndi Spain Europactor Aaecomhel.
